    {
      "chinese": "石板屋在台灣非常特殊，台灣原住民族中，魯凱族與排灣族的Ravare部落有此項建築。魯凱族石板品質最好，真正的頁岩可當立板，或是用於舖地板，石板屋建築是夏天涼爽，冬天溫暖，非常適合在地的氣溫，住宿體驗與其他族群完全不同。政府應當積極研究、協助當地鄉公所和族人研發並宣傳，引進更多人來體驗和觀光。",
      "ab": "Kay Talaalibi kay daane, kathaane kay talaalibi ka nipawkalrivilane ikay Tayvange, ikay ki kacalrisiane, adravane kay Ngubabuculu kay suaravare ka cekele, mathariri kay lrenege ki taliNgudradrekay, amani ku kalrenegane ka saalialibane, saacapadhane, sadralriane, saalibane masudaedalelpenga kay lrenege sidaane ikay ki cekele lini;\r\n [===]\r\nmanganerece lukakaladralrangedrangane, maculu lukakalakecelrane, mamaua ki saseverane si takaculuane ki kadaengane, lupasuladhane lakamuakalrivili ki drumane ka zuku, kadrua ku lrilemethe si matumane iyaana, lakaakisamulane ki suasihu, suagukusiw paralubu ki sakacekele kingikiw kidredreme ku arukitukucingalrane ki wakelakela kay kilrialringaw ki talaalibi.",
      "order": "2",
